## ğŸ¯ Objective
Manipulate SQL queries through user input to access unauthorized data, demonstrating database security vulnerabilities.

## ğŸ“Š SQL Injection Types Explored
| Type | Description | DVWA Level |
|------|-------------|------------|
| **Union-Based** | Combine results from multiple SELECT statements | Low, Medium |
| **Error-Based** | Extract data from database error messages | Low |
| **Boolean Blind** | Infer data from true/false responses | Medium, High |
| **Time-Based** | Use timing delays to extract information | High |

